🔥 4. Scenario-Based Questions
✅ Q: Find duplicate records
SELECT name, COUNT(*)
FROM users
GROUP BY name
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;


✅ Q: Get last 5 records
SELECT * FROM orders
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 5;
✅ Q: Pagination
SELECT * FROM products
LIMIT 10 OFFSET 20;
